    <string name="about_title">About</string>
    <string name="about_text_1">Habit building is a process based on what you do repeatedly. It takes, on average, 66 days to build a habit. Given the time and commitment required, it is difficult to maintain the motivation to keep going.
    </string>
    <string name="about_text_2"><b>Small Steps</b> aims to help you build habits by focusing on small, incremental steps. It is based on the ideas of The 3 Râ€™s of Habit Change: Reminder, Routine, and Reward.
    </string>
    <string name="about_text_3a">A Reminder is the trigger that initiates the behavior.\n\nA Routine is the behavior, itself.\n\nA Reward is the benefit gained from performing the behavior.
    </string>
    <string name="about_text_3b">A Reminder is the trigger that initiates the behavior.\nA Routine is the behavior, itself.\nA Reward is the benefit gained from performing the behavior.
    </string>
    <string name="about_text_4">
        This app uses Reminders to trigger Routines to earn Rewards.
    </string>
    <string name="about_text_5">
        With this process, small steps build big habits!
    </string>
